name: #2 Circle Of Life - Childhood.
description:
SOUND ON!

1/5 pieces from my and his (Dolev Morad) life cycle Dolev is the one that owned what makes your ears jump out during this loop. 

It's the stage of childhood.

The main things are Friends, Joy, Energy,
and first experiences at this stage.

Most of the things that we do at this stage are new to you and exciting.
It reminds us to forget about everything that holds us back and move forward!

Conserve our inner energy!
